,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:48:59.000Z","msg":"好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三歲老豆已經買steinway比佢練<br />\n贏在起跑線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:40:57.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三歲彈三角琴<br />\n又係邊個紅二代黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.kiubear.com/image/cache/catalog/magic_tricks/Children-Toy-Musical-Instrument-Rhythm-Band-Triangle-Educational-Preschool-Toys--3-800x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kiubear.com%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fcatalog%2Fmagic_tricks%2FChildren-Toy-Musical-Instrument-Rhythm-Band-Triangle-Educational-Preschool-Toys--3-800x800.jpg&h=c4d89a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"一部steinway三角琴閒閒地100-200萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有父幹又有天資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}